---
title: Honey Chili-Garlic Roasted Salmon with Pan-Fried Vegetables
description: We're practically drooling over this combination of luscious honey-chili-garlic roasted salmon, a juicy pan-fried veggie jumble and fluffy basmati rice. This is one for the (cook)books, folks!
